The Solution!

ERC721
The new standard for ERC721
Instead of storing files in cloud storage, platform servers or on IPFS, FOIL Proof-of-Stake platform brings to life the reliable and bulletproof Pure NFT

Token data is stored directly on the blockchain, as well as the NFT’s provenance — a complete history.

Pure =
Immutable =
Unchangeable =
Incorruptible

In addition, this solution is fully available for Binance Smart Chain and Ethereum communities as a completely new standard for ERC721.

When creating NFTs on popular marketplace platforms, the original files will be stored on the FOIL blockchain.

Pre-sale
Bounty hunting

Foil Network will hold a seed round private token sale in an Ethereum TGE, where eFOIL ERC20 tokens will be distributed among participants. The crypto sale will take place over a special Token Generation Event smart contract, and it will be limited to a certain number of registered crypto investors.

The eFOIL token is an ERC20 representation of the native FOIL in the Ethereum Network. After the presale of TGE smart contract, the eFoil token can be exchanged to native FOIL on 1:1 basis via FOIL DEX.

The integration of Ethereum blockchain brings more amazing cross-chain possibilities to FOIL’s elastic blockchain functionality.

Foil Networks
Go to wallet
Go to wallet

FOIL SandBox is a fully capable blockchain testnet with different features and functionalities.

The SandBox Web Wallet has all the new features to be launched in the mainnet. Each wallet has an initial amount of FOIL, MVolt and DOGE to process various transactions.

By opening the test crypto wallet, you can create, mint and store NFTs in the blockchain, make bids on NFT Marketplace and get test coins on your FOIL account balance, all for free.

SandBox
MainNet

The mainnet has the following BaaS services implemented: tokenization, DeFi and crypto staking, NFT, KYC and AML, e-Voting, DAO, on-chain storage, and more.

To provide high security, important transactions, such as creating digital assets and statuses, are possible only with on-chain KYC verification. In a cross-chain interaction, by using smart-bridges, it’s possible to deposit and withdraw BTC, LTC, DASH and DOGE. In the future, other cryptocurrencies will be connected to Foil Network, like ETH and BNB.

Use the advanced features of the FOIL blockchain directly from anywhere. FOIL Web Wallet supports payments, NFT minting and storage, Marketplace and integrated DEX along with already integrated Bitcoin, Litecoin, DASH and DOGE.

About

FOIL Network is a new standard
﻿of interoperable and elastic Blockchain-as-a-service (BaaS) technology. It focuses on establishing a credible system for verified identities of investors, contributors, community members, validators and counterparties based on immutable and transparent blockchain technology.

Pitchdeck
Whitepaper

FOIL Network is a PoS/LPoS/DPoS blockchain built on Java. It is a scalable, interoperable and multifunctional blockchain network protocol, which serves as a platform for creating unique decentralized economies within a multi-tier distributed, autonomous, and circular ecosystem. FOIL as a Blockchain-as-a-Service technology, is designed to improve the integration of blockchain for real world applications.

Digital ID

With FOIL it is possible to completely own your personal data. The platform technology is secured by on-chain identity verification. FOIL Network provides the possibility to have a verified anonymous account and a verified digital ID account in a single wallet. Thus, AML/KYC can be easily performed, recorded and maintained on the blockchain.

Tokenomics
Foil
Mvolt

FOIL is the official native digital accounting unit that gives its holder additional rights to manage and govern the ecosystem.

It is a stable token and the energy of theplatform. FOIL Network charges MVolt for the operations, preventing the abuse of node resources. It is used to pay for transactions, and it is given as a reward for building blocks.

The Dual Token
crypto economy

FOIL Network is based on two accounting units - Foil and MVolt. This model allows users to participate in the ecosystem without reducing their stake in the network.
It separates the rights of governance from the rights of using the network. It also provides the means to acquire the tokens required to pay transaction fees, which increases the economic efficiency of the platform.

• Perform on-chain creator transactions

Dogecoin

Why DOGE?

Foil Network support dogecoin, as the most simple and scalable cryptocurrency with huge supply and emission, top liquidity and global crypto adopters recognition. You can use dogecoin throughout the Foil Blockchain: buy FOIL and mVolt, pay for NFTs and process exchanges just like with native FOIL tokens. The integration of DOGE brings FOIL elastic blockchain as a liquid custodian and staking capabilities provider, because of the extended DeFi features of the Foil Network.
